snippet.title: [GOTY 2014 #4] Best VGM 1723 - Legend of Grimrock II - The Master and the Apprentice
snippet.description:
Soundtrack: https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/legend-grimrock-2-original/id933238227

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
Legend of Grimrock II (2014)
Master and The Apprentice
Scoring Helsinki
